{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Little Chef 2</i></strong> invites you back into the kitchen for a delightful cooking adventure filled with <strong>cozy vibes</strong> and <strong>whimsical fu</strong>n! Whether you're a seasoned chef or just here for the laughs, this adorable sequel brings joy to every dish you create!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PHYSICS BASED</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/PhysicsShowcase.gif?t=1734541225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy physics-based interactions as you unleash your creativity across a variety of kitchens and charming settings. Grab ingredients and objects from the scene and toss them around at your will.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>OVER 150 UNIQUE DISHES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/DishesShowcase.gif?t=1734541225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No matter what you end up cooking, a huge variety of possible dishes make every ingredient count and allow you to throw anything into the pot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CUTE &amp; HIDDEN INTERACTIONS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/InteractionsShowcase.gif?t=1734541225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Click around in the different hand illustrated scenes to find out what cute little easter eggs and quirky interactions await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>THREE DISTINCT KITCHENS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/LevelShowcase.gif?t=1734541225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock three different hand crafted kitchens which all offer their own new ingredients and ways of cooking, making sure you never end up cooking the same things again and again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3376500?t=1734541225","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1734541225","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/48b932e867027ae9b91c54d5cc19d0086b8cb5e8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734541225","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/48b932e867027ae9b91c54d5cc19d0086b8cb5e8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734541225","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Little Chef 2</i></strong> invites you back into the kitchen for a delightful cooking adventure filled with <strong>cozy vibes</strong> and <strong>whimsical fu</strong>n! Whether you're a seasoned chef or just here for the laughs, this adorable sequel brings joy to every dish you create!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PHYSICS BASED</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376500/extras/PhysicsShowcase.gif?t=1734541225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy physics-based interactions as you unleash your creativity across a variety of kitchens and charming settings. Grab ingredients and objects from the scene and toss them around at your will.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><str